				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">Well, I have been in a couple of groups now... Still only level 8 though, and I have noticed that my primary mission has almost always been as a healer in larger groups, so I'm thinking of maybe changing my way and go full at Nurture/Regrowth... I've heard though that Bards should have the healing abilities in the game? Not sure about that one though, just heard it from a higher level Bard, he was around 30-35 or so.
<br />

<br />
But honestly Moshkiae, don't you think that the high-end of the game requires people that can AE mez mobs, to keep crowd control, that would seriously make the job easier for the healers, which are needed, and make them able to concentrate more on one person?</span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
			</tr>
